    "causal_summary": "Two dispatch-path failures — a manual opencode run with no stdin redirect that hung at 0% CPU, and a fanout lineage that stalled at 0 iterations with no terminal event — both trace to the same shape: a machine check that would have caught it exists or is nearly free, but nothing in the execution path runs it before the risky action. This is a plan-only design for wiring those checks in.",
